TO EMIGRATE.

227
00:09:39,012 --> 00:09:40,212
THEN YOU
SHAKE THE HUSBANDS DOWN.

228
00:09:40,247 --> 00:09:42,077
AND IF THEY DON'T PAY,

229
00:09:42,115 --> 00:09:44,075
