TO YOU, ROGER?

237
00:09:56,096 --> 00:09:58,896
IT DOES,
AS A MATTER OF FACT.

238
00:09:58,932 --> 00:10:01,232
I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT
KIDNAPPING OR PROSTITUTION.

239
00:10:01,268 --> 00:10:04,038
AND IF YOU ASK ME,
OLENA WENT BACK TO UKRAINE.

240
00:10:04,071 --> 00:10:06,111
