RIGHT?

251
00:10:29,963 --> 00:10:33,933
THERE IS AN INNOCENT YOUNG GIRL
MISSING WHO CAME TO THIS COUNTRY

252
00:10:33,967 --> 00:10:35,267
TRYING TO MAKE A BETTER LIFE
FOR HERSELF.

253
00:10:35,302 --> 00:10:37,242
YOU ARE RESPONSIBLE
FOR BRINGING HER HERE,

254
