AND YOU COULDN'T BE BOTHERED
TO HELP HER WHEN SHE ASKED.

255
00:10:41,141 --> 00:10:43,111
WHAT DO YOU WANT
FROM ME?

256
00:10:43,143 --> 00:10:46,053
I WANT THE NAME OF THE MAN
WHO WAS SHAKING FRANK DOWN.

257
00:10:46,079 --> 00:10:48,119
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
THAT I --

258
00:10:48,148 --> 00:10:51,148
