THIS PLACE IS GONNA BE SWARMING

259
00:10:51,184 --> 00:10:54,094
WITH I.C.E. AGENTS,
U.S. ATTORNEYS, I.R.S.

260
00:10:54,121 --> 00:10:56,191
YOU WILL GO TO FEDERAL PRISON,
KICKING YOURSELF

261
00:10:56,223 --> 00:10:59,063
FOR NOT COOPERATING
WITH THAT NICE GIRL FROM THE FBI

262
00:10:59,092 --> 00:11:00,162
WHEN YOU HAD THE CHANCE.

263
00:11:02,329 --> 00:11:06,099
Kate:
YURI PETROVICH?

264
00:11:06,133 --> 00:11:07,303
SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI,
FBI.

265
00:11:07,334 --> 00:11:08,974
OH, FBI, HUH?

266
00:11:09,002 --> 00:11:11,172
I MUST BE
MOVING UP IN THE WORLD.

267
00:11:11,204 --> 00:11:13,274
WE'RE LOOKING FOR A MISSING
WOMAN -- OLENA PRENTICE.

268
00:11:13,306 --> 00:11:15,176
