YOU'RE THE, UH, FAMOUS
SELF-HELP SAGE TO THE STARS.

286
00:11:56,049 --> 00:11:59,049
WELL, MY ACADEMIC SPECIALTY'S
BEHAVIORAL SCIENCE, OF COURSE.

287
