BUT IT MOVED SOME BOOKS,
SO WHAT DO I KNOW?

290
00:12:04,191 --> 00:12:07,031
YOU KNOW, MICHAEL'S HAD
A NEW YORK TIMES BESTSELLER

291
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:08,030
THREE YEARS RUNNING.

292
00:12:08,061 --> 00:12:09,361
IS THAT RIGHT?

293
00:12:09,396 --> 00:12:11,196
I'VE READ ALL YOUR BOOKS.

294
00:12:11,231 --> 00:12:12,371
YEAH, IN FACT,
WHEN PAUL RANG WITH HIS OFFER,

295
00:12:12,399 --> 00:12:14,129
