I'D ONLY CONSIDER IT

296
00:12:14,167 --> 00:12:16,037
IF IT MEANT A CHANCE
TO WORK WITH YOU.

297
00:12:16,069 --> 00:12:18,409
UH, I READ
YOUR LAST BOOK, TOO.

298
00:12:23,243 --> 00:12:24,343
IT WAS BRILLIANT...

299
00:12:24,377 --> 00:12:26,077
W-WASN'T IT, DANIEL?

300
00:12:26,113 --> 00:12:27,283
NO. NO.

301
00:12:27,314 --> 00:12:30,254
I-I THOUGHT IT WAS A MUDDLED
MESS OF SHODDY RESEARCH,

302
00:12:30,283 --> 00:12:32,223
JUNK SCIENCE,
AND PEDANTIC PLATITUDES,

303
00:12:32,252 --> 00:12:34,252
BUT I HOPE YOU ENJOY
YOUR TIME IN CHICAGO.

304
00:12:34,287 --> 00:12:37,287
IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME, I HAVE SOME
ACTUAL SCHOLARSHIP TO ATTEND TO.

305
00:12:39,192 --> 00:12:40,232
RIGHT.

306
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:42,360
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYS ]

307
00:12:44,431 --> 00:12:46,231
DOC.

308
00:12:46,266 --> 00:12:48,166
OH, I WENT
TO THE [BLEEP] MEETING.

309
00:12:48,201 --> 00:12:50,171
WHAT THE [BLEEP] ELSE
DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

310
00:12:50,203 --> 00:12:51,373
AGENT MORETTI CALLED,

311
00:12:51,404 --> 00:12:53,314
