TO HELP I.D. A SUSPECT.

312
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:55,080
[ SIGHS ]

313
00:12:55,108 --> 00:12:57,408
ALL RIGHT. GET THE CAR.
I'LL GET MY COAT.

314
00:13:03,283 --> 00:13:06,223
