HELLO, DR. PIERCE.

315
00:13:07,454 --> 00:13:09,094
MAY I HELP YOU?

316
00:13:09,122 --> 00:13:12,232
MAYBE I CAN HELP YOU,
PROFESSOR.

317
00:13:13,293 --> 00:13:16,263
FRIENDLY ADVICE --
WON'T COST YOU NOTHING.

318
00:13:16,296 --> 00:13:20,396
IT'S BETTER FOR EVERYONE --
YOU, ESPECIALLY --

319
00:13:20,433 --> 00:13:24,203
IF YOU DON'T HELP FBI
ON THIS CASE NO MORE.

320
00:13:24,237 --> 00:13:26,107
[ SCOFFS ]

321
00:13:26,139 --> 00:13:27,309
HOW DO YOU KNOW I'M...

322
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:31,380
WE HAVE MANY FRIENDS,
EVEN AT FBI.

323
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,410
YOU HAVE A MOLE.

324
00:13:34,447 --> 00:13:36,277
[ CHUCKLES ]

325
00:13:36,316 --> 00:13:37,346
A MOLE.

326
00:13:37,384 --> 00:13:40,124
WE'RE NOT KGB,
BUT, YES...

327
00:13:40,153 --> 00:13:42,393
I SUPPOSE
YOU COULD SAY THIS.

328
00:13:44,491 --> 00:13:49,261
I HEAR YOU ARE
A VERY SMART MAN, PROFESSOR.

329
00:13:49,296 --> 00:13:54,166
SO I THINK YOU KNOW
IT IS NOT HEALTHY

330
00:13:54,201 --> 00:13:55,501
FOR YOU TO WORK
WITH THESE PEOPLE.

331
00:13:58,171 --> 00:14:03,411
AFTER ALL, YOU DON'T WANT
TO ALSO DISAPPEAR, DO YOU?

332
00:14:06,479 --> 00:14:08,519
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

333
00:14:15,022 --> 00:14:17,162
DO ANY OF THESE MEN
REMIND YOU OF THE MAN

334
00:14:17,190 --> 00:14:19,160
WHO THREATENED
TO HURT YOUR WIFE?

335
00:14:19,192 --> 00:14:23,232
ANYTHING STAND OUT?
HANDS, HAIRLINE, POSTURE?

336
00:14:28,235 --> 00:14:30,035
NUMBER 2.

337
00:14:30,070 --> 00:14:31,140
WHY HIM?

338
00:14:31,171 --> 00:14:33,171
I RECOGNIZE
THAT WIDOW'S PEAK,

339
00:14:33,206 --> 00:14:35,206
THOSE SCRAWNY,
BOWED LEGS.

340
00:14:35,242 --> 00:14:38,112
I WANT THAT [BLEEP] TO PAY
FOR WHAT HE DID TO MY WIFE.

341
00:14:38,145 --> 00:14:40,875
Kate: THAT'S GOOD. IT'S THE SAME
GUY WHOSE VOICE YOU I.D.'d.

342
00:14:40,914 --> 00:14:43,224
DANIEL, CAN YOU TESTIFY IN COURT
THAT THE VISUAL I.D. IS VALID

343
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:47,020
DESPITE MR. PRENTICE'S
CONDITION?

344
00:14:47,054 --> 00:14:49,224
DANIEL. YES OR NO?
IS THE I.D. SOLID?

345
00:14:49,256 --> 00:14:51,956
YES, I -- I'LL STAND BY IT.

346
00:14:54,962 --> 00:14:57,062
I'M GONNA LAY IT OUT
FOR YOU, YURI.

347
00:14:57,097 --> 00:15:02,297
YOU GOT PRIORS --
PIMPING, EXTORTION, ASSAULT.

348
00:15:02,335 --> 00:15:04,135
FRANK PRENTICE
JUST FINGERED YOU

349
00:15:04,171 --> 00:15:06,211
AS THE MAN WHO THREATENED
TO ABDUCT HIS WIFE.

350
00:15:06,239 --> 00:15:08,039
SHE DISAPPEARED.
NOW SHE'S DEAD.

351
00:15:08,075 --> 00:15:12,905
WHAT DO YOU MAKE?
$40,000, $45,000 A YEAR?

352
00:15:12,946 --> 00:15:15,216
YOU'RE A HOT
LITTLE SPINNER.

353
00:15:15,248 --> 00:15:18,148
COME WORK FOR ME.
YOU COULD EARN SOME REAL MONEY.

354
00:15:18,185 --> 00:15:21,145
AN INNOCENT GIRL
WAS KILLED, YURI.

355
00:15:21,188 --> 00:15:24,018
NOW, IN ADDITION TO THE FACT
THAT IT REALLY [BLEEP] ME OFF,

356
00:15:24,057 --> 00:15:26,187
IT'S ALSO MURDER DURING
THE COMMISSION OF A FELONY.

357
00:15:26,226 --> 00:15:28,956
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS?

358
00:15:28,996 --> 00:15:30,196
DEATH PENALTY.

359
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:33,100
AND I FOR ONE AM NOT GONNA
BE CRYING AT YOUR FUNERAL.

360
00:15:36,136 --> 00:15:38,936
BUT MAYBE...

361
00:15:38,972 --> 00:15:41,942
YOU DIDN'T
MEAN TO KILL HER.

362
00:15:41,975 --> 00:15:43,235
YEAH, THE MEDICAL
EXAMINER SAYS

363
00:15:43,276 --> 00:15:46,246
THAT SHE DIED FROM A BLOW
TO THE BASE OF THE SKULL.

364
00:15:46,279 --> 00:15:48,279
MAYBE SHE WAS
TRYING TO GET AWAY.

365
00:15:48,315 --> 00:15:51,115
MAYBE SHE FELL,
HIT HER HEAD.

366
00:15:51,151 --> 00:15:53,121
NOW YOU'RE ONLY LOOKING
AT INVOLUNTARY MANSLAUGHTER.

367
00:15:53,153 --> 00:15:55,123
YOU MIGHT ONLY DO
18 MONTHS.

368
00:15:55,155 --> 00:15:58,125
YOU'RE OFFERING ME A DEAL,
JUST 'CAUSE YOU'RE SWEET ON ME?

369
00:15:58,158 --> 00:16:00,058
YOU'RE TOO SMALL
FOR ME, YURI --

370
00:16:00,093 --> 00:16:02,033
IN MORE WAYS THAN ONE,
I WOULD BET.

371
00:16:03,030 --> 00:16:04,200
[ SCOFFS ]

372
00:16:04,231 --> 00:16:06,971
NO, I WANT
SOMETHING BIGGER.

373
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,300
I WANT ALEXEI TUPELOV.

374
00:16:08,335 --> 00:16:10,295
OH. [ CHUCKLES ]

375
00:16:10,337 --> 00:16:12,237
[BLEEP]
WHAT ARE YOU SMOKING?

376
00:16:12,272 --> 00:16:15,142
I RAT OUT TUPELOV, I MIGHT
AS WELL GET THE DEATH PENALTY.

377
00:16:15,175 --> 00:16:16,305
OKAY.

378
00:16:16,343 --> 00:16:19,083
WE'VE ALREADY GOT YOU
ON THE EXTORTION.

379
00:16:19,112 --> 00:16:22,082
IT'S UP TO FIVE YEARS
FOR EACH COUNT.

380
00:16:22,115 --> 00:16:24,345
I HOPE YOU ENJOY
YOUR STAY AT MARION.

381
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:29,220
Roger: DO YOU THINK
HE'S GONNA GIVE US TUPELOV?

382
00:16:29,256 --> 00:16:32,156
IT WOULD HELP IF WE COULD
CONNECT HIM TO THE CRIME SCENE.

383
00:16:32,192 --> 00:16:33,992
ANY LUCK
ON THE BLUE CAMARO?

384
00:16:34,027 --> 00:16:35,997
YURI DRIVES AN [ SIGHS ]

385
00:16:36,029 --> 00:16:38,299
I DOUBT YURI AND HIS BOYS
WOULD BE STUPID ENOUGH

386
00:16:38,331 --> 00:16:42,341
TO COMMIT KIDNAPPING
IN A REGISTERED CAR.

387
00:16:42,369 --> 00:16:45,139
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYS ]

388
00:16:52,279 --> 00:16:54,149
EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT,
DR. PIERCE?

389
00:16:54,181 --> 00:16:56,051
YES, I'M FINE.

390
00:16:59,152 --> 00:17:00,352
THAT PENDANT.

391
00:17:00,387 --> 00:17:03,257
YURI PETROVICH
HAS ONE JUST LIKE IT.

392
00:17:03,290 --> 00:17:06,330
WELL, I GREW UP WITH A LOT
OF THE GUYS IN TUPELOV'S CREW.

393
00:17:06,359 --> 00:17:09,159
THAT'S WHY I WAS PICKED
FOR THE TASK FORCE.

394
00:17:10,397 --> 00:17:13,327
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

395
00:17:13,366 --> 00:17:17,066
DID YURI
REALLY KILL OLENA?

396
00:17:18,171 --> 00:17:20,171
WHO ELSE
COULD HAVE DONE IT?

397
00:17:20,207 --> 00:17:23,077
WELL, LET'S JUST SAY
SOME FRIENDS OF MINE
WOULD BE VERY GRATEFUL

398
00:17:23,110 --> 00:17:25,350
IF YOU DIDN'T HELP MORETTI
PIN THIS MURDER ON YURI.

399
00:17:26,479 --> 00:17:28,219
YOU'RE THE MOLE.

400
00:17:28,248 --> 00:17:31,048
NO. NOT ME, PROFESSOR.

401
00:17:31,084 --> 00:17:33,394
BUT YOU'RE RIGHT.
THERE IS A MOLE.

402
00:17:33,420 --> 00:17:35,360
WHO?

403
00:17:37,390 --> 00:17:39,090
DANIEL.

404
00:17:41,094 --> 00:17:43,064
GIVE YOU A LIFT BACK?

405
00:17:43,096 --> 00:17:44,056
YEAH.

406
00:17:44,097 --> 00:17:45,367
SURE..

407
00:17:48,135 --> 00:17:51,065
Natalie: YOU'RE BEING THREATENED
BY A RUSSIAN MOBSTER,

408
00:17:51,104 --> 00:17:53,214
AND YOU DON'T BOTHER
MENTIONING IT TO KATE?

409
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,410
WHY NOT?

410
00:17:54,441 --> 00:17:57,311
'CAUSE HE'S PROBABLY
A [BLEEP] HALLUCINATION --

411
00:17:57,344 --> 00:18:00,384
THE SAME AS THE LADY AGENT
TURNED OUT TO BE.

412
00:18:00,413 --> 00:18:04,183
I JUST -- I DON'T WANT KATE
TO THINK I'M BONKERS.

413
00:18:04,217 --> 00:18:05,487
WELL, IF YOU'RE SO CONVINCED
THAT HE WASN'T REAL,

414
00:18:05,518 --> 00:18:07,248
why do you keep looking
out the window?!

415
00:18:07,287 --> 00:18:09,217
Because I might be wrong!

416
00:18:09,256 --> 00:18:11,116
W-what if there really is
a goon out there

417
00:18:11,158 --> 00:18:12,388
waiting to break
my kneecaps?

418
00:18:12,425 --> 00:18:16,195
DANIEL, YOU AND I BOTH KNOW
THAT FEELING THREATENED

419
00:18:16,229 --> 00:18:19,099
BY A CRIMINAL CONSPIRACY
STRAIGHT OUT OF A SPY NOVEL

420
00:18:19,132 --> 00:18:21,402
IS CLASSIC
SCHIZOPHRENIC DELUSION.

421
00:18:21,434 --> 00:18:25,414
