THAT THERE'S A FIENDISH PLOT

422
00:18:25,438 --> 00:18:28,378
WITH MOBSTERS
AND CORRUPT FBI AGENTS

423
00:18:28,408 --> 00:18:30,278
OR THAT YOU'RE
IMAGINING IT?

424
00:18:36,449 --> 00:18:38,289
THANK YOU
FOR BEING HERE.

425
00:18:38,318 --> 00:18:40,248
THAT'S WHAT FRIENDS
ARE FOR.

426
00:18:40,287 --> 00:18:43,457
YOU SAID THIS THUG TOLD YOU
THAT IT WASN'T HEALTHY

427
00:18:43,490 --> 00:18:46,390
FOR YOU TO KEEP WORKING
FOR THE FBI.

428
00:18:46,426 --> 00:18:49,126
IT SOUNDS LIKE A MANIFESTATION
OF YOUR ANXIETY

429
00:18:49,162 --> 00:18:51,162
ABOUT GETTING INVOLVED
WITH THESE CASES,

430
00:18:51,198 --> 00:18:53,298
BECAUSE YOU KNOW
THEY GET YOU OFF YOUR ROUTINE

431
00:18:53,333 --> 00:18:55,133
AND TRIGGER EPISODES.

432
00:18:55,168 --> 00:18:58,168
HE ALSO SAID I MIGHT DISAPPEAR.
WHAT'S THAT ABOUT?

433
00:18:58,205 --> 00:19:00,365
LAST TIME YOU
CHECKED INTO REXFORD,

434
00:19:00,407 --> 00:19:02,277
YOU DIDN'T TELL ANYBODY
WHERE YOU WERE --

435
00:19:02,309 --> 00:19:04,139
YOUR FRIENDS,
YOUR STUDENTS.

436
00:19:04,177 --> 00:19:07,177
YOU JUST DISAPPEARED
OUT OF THEIR LIVES.

437
00:19:07,214 --> 00:19:10,154
SO, I'M NOT AFRAID
OF UKRAINIAN GANGSTERS

438
00:19:10,183 --> 00:19:13,193
SO MUCH AS ORDERLIES
WITH BUTTERFLY NETS?

439
00:19:14,321 --> 00:19:17,161
YOU'RE NOT GOING BACK
TO THE HOSPITAL.

440
00:19:17,190 --> 00:19:18,460
YOU HAVE ME,
YOU HAVE LEWICKI,

441
00:19:18,491 --> 00:19:20,491
AND YOU'RE MANAGING
YOUR CONDITION.

442
00:19:20,527 --> 00:19:22,257
[ SIGHS ]

443
00:19:22,295 --> 00:19:25,265
SOME DAYS I MANAGE
BETTER THAN OTHERS.

444
00:19:25,298 --> 00:19:27,428
YOUR SYMPTOMS ARE MORE ACUTE
WHEN YOUR SUBCONSCIOUS

445
00:19:27,467 --> 00:19:30,237
IS WORKING ON A PROBLEM
THAT IT CAN'T QUITE SOLVE.

446
00:19:31,538 --> 00:19:35,208
THE UKRAINIAN GUY
SAID THERE WAS A MOLE.

447
00:19:35,242 --> 00:19:37,512
NOW, IT'S NOT THE AGENT,
OBVIOUSLY.

448
00:19:37,544 --> 00:19:40,184
WELL, MAYBE IT'S A RIDDLE.
WHAT'S A MOLE?

449
00:19:40,213 --> 00:19:44,453
A SPY, AN IMPOSTER, SOMEONE
WHO HIDES IN PLAIN SIGHT.

450
00:19:44,484 --> 00:19:47,294
BUT THERE'S
ANOTHER KIND OF MOLE --

451
00:19:47,320 --> 00:19:50,220
THE KIND THAT BURROWS
UNDERGROUND.

452
00:19:51,391 --> 00:19:52,461
MOLES ARE BLIND.

453
00:19:52,492 --> 00:19:54,192
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

454
00:19:54,227 --> 00:19:56,227
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT TIME IT IS?

455
00:19:56,263 --> 00:19:58,373
YURI DIDN'T KILL
OLENA PRENTICE.

456
00:19:58,398 --> 00:20:00,298
WHAT?

457
00:20:00,333 --> 00:20:03,443
YOU WOKE ME UP AT...

458
00:20:03,470 --> 00:20:06,310
3:18 A.M.

459
00:20:06,339 --> 00:20:08,379
TO ACCUSE ME
OF TRYING TO COERCE A CONFESSION

460
00:20:08,408 --> 00:20:09,508
OUT OF AN INNOCENT MAN?

461
00:20:09,542 --> 00:20:11,382
THAT SCUMBAG
IS ANYTHING BUT INNOCENT,

462
00:20:11,411 --> 00:20:13,351
BUT THAT DOES NOT MAKE HIM
THE KILLER.

463
00:20:14,514 --> 00:20:15,554
OKAY, DANIEL.

464
00:20:15,582 --> 00:20:17,622
IF THE LYING, PIMPING,
SADISTIC FELON

465
00:20:17,650 --> 00:20:21,450
WHO THREATENED TO ABDUCT OLENA
DIDN'T KILL HER, THEN WHO DID?

466
00:20:21,488 --> 00:20:22,518
HER HUSBAND.

467
00:20:22,555 --> 00:20:24,515
HE PASSED A POLYGRAPH.

468
00:20:24,557 --> 00:20:25,527
HE'S FACE-BLIND!

469
00:20:25,558 --> 00:20:27,388
FOR ALL WE KNOW, HE --

470
00:20:27,427 --> 00:20:29,527
HE KILLED HIS OWN WIFE
WITHOUT REALIZING IT WAS HER.

471
00:20:29,562 --> 00:20:33,332
BUT YOU JUST PROVED THAT
PROSOPAGNOSIACS CAN I.D. PEOPLE

472
00:20:33,366 --> 00:20:36,236
BY THEIR VOICE OR THEIR POSTURE
OR WHATEVER.

473
00:20:36,269 --> 00:20:38,369
HE WOULD HAVE KNOWN
HIS OWN WIFE.

474
00:20:38,405 --> 00:20:41,235
MAYBE SHE WAS WEARING
SOME KIND OF DISGUISE.

475
00:20:41,274 --> 00:20:44,284
[ Laughing ] WHAT IS THIS?
IS THIS, LIKE, A SPY NOVEL?

476
00:20:44,311 --> 00:20:46,581
DON'T -- I'M JUST...

477
00:20:46,613 --> 00:20:48,553
I'M JUST SAYING --
I'M JUST SAYING IT'S POSSIBLE.

478
00:20:48,581 --> 00:20:50,351
OKAY, DANIEL.

479
00:20:50,383 --> 00:20:52,253
WHY WOULD OLENA
HAVE BEEN WEARING A DISGUISE?

480
00:20:52,285 --> 00:20:54,415
I DON'T KNOW. MAYBE SHE
WAS TRYING TO GET AWAY FROM HIM.

481
00:20:54,454 --> 00:20:55,594
YOU SAID YOURSELF
HOW AWFUL HE IS.

482
00:20:55,622 --> 00:20:59,292
THE MARRIAGE BROKER DID SAY
THAT SHE WANTED OUT.

483
00:20:59,326 --> 00:21:02,426
YOU SEE? YOU SEE?
SO SHE RUNS AWAY.

484
00:21:02,462 --> 00:21:06,372
FRANK REALIZES THAT -- THAT
HIS PRIZED POSSESSION IS GONE,

485
00:21:06,399 --> 00:21:08,539
AFTER ALL THE DEBT HE'S RUN UP
AND THREATS HE'S ENDURED

486
00:21:08,568 --> 00:21:10,438
FROM YURI --
ALL OF IT FOR HER.

487
00:21:10,470 --> 00:21:12,440
SO HE TRACKS THE UNGRATEFUL
[BLEEP] DOWN, AND HE KILLS HER.

488
00:21:12,472 --> 00:21:14,612
EXCEPT THERE'S A FLAW
IN YOUR THEORY.

489
00:21:14,641 --> 00:21:17,541
IF FRANK KILLED HIS WIFE FOR THE
REASONS THAT YOU JUST LAID OUT,

490
00:21:17,577 --> 00:21:20,277
HE WOULD HAVE KNOWN THAT IT WAS
HER WHO HE WAS KILLING,

491
00:21:20,313 --> 00:21:22,283
AND HE WOULDN'T HAVE PASSED
A POLY, FACE-BLIND OR NOT.

492
00:21:22,315 --> 00:21:23,445
RIGHT.

493
00:21:23,483 --> 00:21:25,623
SO, UH, FRANK THOUGHT
SHE WAS KIDNAPPED,

494
00:21:25,652 --> 00:21:28,462
SO MAYBE HE DIDN'T REALIZE
THAT SHE'D RUN AWAY

495
00:21:28,488 --> 00:21:30,518
UNTIL AFTER
HE TOOK THE POLYGRAPH.

496
00:21:30,557 --> 00:21:32,587
THEN -- THEN
HE FIGURES OUT THE TRUTH,

497
00:21:32,625 --> 00:21:35,285
AND HE TRACKS HER DOWN,
AND HE KILLS HER.

498
00:21:35,328 --> 00:21:36,528
NICE.

499
00:21:36,563 --> 00:21:39,473
EXCEPT THE MEDICAL EXAMINER
PUTS HER TIME OF DEATH

500
00:21:39,499 --> 00:21:40,599
BEFORE HE TOOK THE EXAM.

501
00:21:40,633 --> 00:21:42,543
OKAY.
SO -- SO -- THE -- THE --

502
00:21:42,569 --> 00:21:45,569
OKAY. FORGET IT.
FORGET IT. FORGET IT.

503
00:21:45,605 --> 00:21:47,565
NO, I JUST -- YOU KNOW --
GO -- GO BACK TO THAT.

504
00:21:47,607 --> 00:21:50,407
I'M SURE YOU'LL SLEEP THE SLEEP
OF THE JUST KNOWING THAT --

505
00:21:50,443 --> 00:21:51,613
THAT THE PUZZLE'S
BEEN SOLVED

506
00:21:51,644 --> 00:21:54,314
AND THAT YOU'VE NAILED
THE RIGHT GUY FOR THE MURDER.

507
00:21:54,347 --> 00:21:55,647
WELL, I AM AWAKE ALREADY.

508
00:21:55,682 --> 00:21:57,522
WELL, THEN, LET'S GO.

509
00:21:58,585 --> 00:22:00,515
I'M GONNA
PUT SOME PANTS ON FIRST.

510
00:22:04,357 --> 00:22:05,527
YOUR APARTMENT'S NICE.

511
00:22:09,796 --> 00:22:11,496
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

512
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:15,370
[ Slavic accent ]
MAY I HELP YOU?

513
00:22:15,402 --> 00:22:17,772
SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI, FBI.
THIS IS DR. PIERCE.

514
00:22:17,804 --> 00:22:21,614
AND YOU ARE, UH, MASHA, THE
PRENTICES' HOUSEKEEPER, CORRECT?

515
00:22:21,641 --> 00:22:22,611
YES.

516
00:22:22,642 --> 00:22:23,712
COME IN.

517
00:22:25,712 --> 00:22:30,752
SO, YOU'RE THE ONE WHO FOUND
MR. PRENTICE UNCONSCIOUS?

518
00:22:30,783 --> 00:22:31,753
YES.

519
00:22:31,784 --> 00:22:34,654
COME HOME FROM MOVIES.

520
00:22:34,687 --> 00:22:37,717
SEE HIM ON FLOOR
WITH BLOOD.

521
00:22:39,626 --> 00:22:40,756
FIRST I THINK
HE IS DEAD.

522
00:22:40,793 --> 00:22:42,503
AND OLENA?

523
00:22:42,529 --> 00:22:43,629
I CALL AMBULANCE.

524
00:22:43,663 --> 00:22:45,773
THEN I LOOK FOR HER.
SHE'S NOT HERE.

525
00:22:45,798 --> 00:22:47,668
I SEE
YOU'RE PACKING.

526
00:22:47,700 --> 00:22:50,700
I SEND OLENA'S CLOTHES
TO HER SISTERS IN UKRAINE,

527
00:22:50,737 --> 00:22:52,467
THEN I FIND OTHER JOB.

528
00:22:52,505 --> 00:22:54,705
YOU WON'T BE STAYING ON
WITH MR. PRENTICE?

529
00:22:54,741 --> 00:23:00,611
OLENA SPEAK LITTLE ENGLISH.
THEY HIRE ME SO I TRANSLATE.

530
00:23:00,647 --> 00:23:02,547
NOW SHE'S GONE.

531
00:23:02,582 --> 00:23:05,492
OLENA DIDN'T HAVE ANY FAMILY
HERE IN THE STATES?

532
00:23:05,518 --> 00:23:08,558
SHE HAVE COUSIN --
PAULINA.

533
00:23:08,588 --> 00:23:11,788
SHE COME HERE TO VISIT
BEFORE I WORK HERE,

534
00:23:11,824 --> 00:23:15,804
BUT MR. PRENTICE NOT LIKE HER,
TELL HER TO GO AWAY.

535
00:23:15,828 --> 00:23:19,628
DOESN'T SOUND LIKE OLENA WAS
VERY HAPPY WITH MR. PRENTICE.

536
00:23:19,666 --> 00:23:22,436
MR. PRENTICE
NOT LET HER GO ANYWHERE.

537
00:23:22,469 --> 00:23:26,439
HE SAY IT IS NOT SAFE, BUT
HE WORK ALWAYS UNTIL VERY LATE.

538
00:23:26,473 --> 00:23:29,583
UNTIL I COME,
OLENA WAS ALONE.

539
00:23:32,479 --> 00:23:33,749
DID HE EVER HURT HER?

540
00:23:35,482 --> 00:23:36,752
SOMETIMES HE HIT HER.

541
00:23:42,489 --> 00:23:45,659
DO YOU THINK IT'S POSSIBLE
SHE WASN'T KIDNAPPED --

542
00:23:45,692 --> 00:23:47,462
THAT MAYBE SHE RAN AWAY?

543
00:23:47,494 --> 00:23:48,734
BUT...

544
00:23:48,761 --> 00:23:52,471
THERE WAS UKRAINIAN MAN ARRESTED
FOR HER MURDER, NO?

545
00:23:52,499 --> 00:23:53,729
DANIEL.

546
00:23:57,704 --> 00:23:59,844
"THANKS FOR
TAKING CARE OF THIS, BABY.

547
00:23:59,872 --> 00:24:02,612
HUGS AND KISSES.
JOLENE."

548
00:24:02,642 --> 00:24:03,882
WHO'S JOLENE?

549
00:24:05,745 --> 00:24:07,675
I NEVER HEAR THIS NAME.

550
00:24:07,714 --> 00:24:10,884
WELL, WHOEVER SHE IS, FRANK'S
PAYING HER CREDIT-CARD BILLS.

551
00:24:17,590 --> 00:24:18,490
[ DOOR OPENS ]

552
00:24:18,525 --> 00:24:19,785
JOLENE GREY?

553
00:24:19,826 --> 00:24:22,696
I'M SPECIAL AGENT MORETTI.
THIS IS DR. DANIEL PIERCE.

554
00:24:22,729 --> 00:24:24,729
THANK YOU FOR AGREEING
TO COME TALK TO US.

555
00:24:24,764 --> 00:24:27,504
I'LL TELL YOU WHATEVER
YOU WANT TO KNOW,

556
00:24:27,534 --> 00:24:29,574
BUT, PLEASE,
DON'T TELL MY HUSBAND.

557
00:24:29,602 --> 00:24:30,602
OKAY.

558
00:24:30,637 --> 00:24:32,707
YOU COOPERATE WITH US,

559
00:24:32,739 --> 00:24:35,609
AND, UH, WE'LL DO WHAT WE CAN
TO KEEP THINGS DISCREET.

560
00:24:35,642 --> 00:24:36,812
THANK YOU.

561
00:24:37,910 --> 00:24:42,720
NOW, THIS IS SOME TAB
YOU'VE RUN UP HERE.

562
00:24:42,749 --> 00:24:47,619
FANCY HOTELS, JEWELRY,
CASH ADVANCES.

563
00:24:48,788 --> 00:24:51,518
I LOST MY WALLET
A FEW MONTHS AGO.

564
00:24:51,558 --> 00:24:54,528
SOMEONE MUST HAVE STOLEN MY I.D.
AND OPENED THIS ACCOUNT.

565
00:24:54,561 --> 00:24:55,661
YEAH, SEE,
THAT'S NOT REALLY

566
00:24:55,695 --> 00:24:56,925
THE WAY IDENTITY THEFT
WORKS, JOLENE.

567
00:24:56,963 --> 00:24:58,903
CRIMINALS RUN UP TABS
UNDER SOMEONE ELSE'S NAME,

568
00:24:58,931 --> 00:25:01,631
AND THEN
THEY DON'T PAY THE BILL.

569
00:25:01,668 --> 00:25:04,598
I'M TELLING YOU,
THESE AREN'T MY CHARGES.

570
00:25:04,637 --> 00:25:07,537
MY HUSBAND TOOK AWAY
MY CREDIT CARDS LAST YEAR.

571
00:25:07,574 --> 00:25:09,844
SO YOU GOT ANOTHER ONE --
PAID FOR EVERY MONTH

572
00:25:09,876 --> 00:25:12,746
WITH CHECKS FROM
FRANK PRENTICE'S
BUSINESS ACCOUNT.

573
00:25:12,779 --> 00:25:14,749
I DON'T KNOW
ANY FRANK PRENTICE.

574
00:25:14,781 --> 00:25:16,551
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
GONNA COOPERATE, JOLENE.

575
00:25:16,583 --> 00:25:18,653
NOW, ACCORDING TO
YOUR CELLPHONE RECORDS,

576
00:25:18,685 --> 00:25:20,685
YOU'VE CALLED FRANK
SEVERAL TIMES A DAY

577
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:21,850
FOR THE PAST FEW MONTHS.

578
00:25:21,888 --> 00:25:24,558
I'M ON A FAMILY PLAN.
MY HUSBAND PAYS THE BILL.

579
00:25:24,591 --> 00:25:27,631
SO YOU GOT A SECOND PHONE,
RESERVED FOR A SPECIAL CALLER.

580
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:29,660
AFTER ALL, YOU WOULDN'T WANT
FRANK'S NUMBER

581
00:25:29,696 --> 00:25:30,926
SHOWING UP
ON YOUR HUSBAND'S BILL.

582
00:25:30,963 --> 00:25:34,833
OR MAYBE YOU WERE JEALOUS
OF FRANK'S WIFE.

583
00:25:34,867 --> 00:25:36,797
MAYBE USED
ONE OF THOSE CASH ADVANCES

584
00:25:36,836 --> 00:25:39,566
TO PAY SOMEONE TO MAKE
OLENA PRENTICE DISAPPEAR.

585
00:25:39,606 --> 00:25:41,836
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

586
00:25:41,874 --> 00:25:44,844
CHECK OUT THOSE HEELS.

587
00:25:46,813 --> 00:25:48,883
MUST HAVE COST HER
A FORTUNE.

588
00:25:48,915 --> 00:25:51,775
TELL ME THE TRUTH,
JOLENE.

589
00:25:51,818 --> 00:25:53,588
WHERE DID YOU GET
THOSE SHOES?

590
00:25:53,620 --> 00:25:54,790
DANIEL?

591
00:25:54,821 --> 00:25:55,821
THEY'RE BEAUTIFUL.

592
00:25:57,023 --> 00:25:59,793
THANK YOU.
MARSHALL FIELD'S.

593
00:25:59,826 --> 00:26:01,586
DID YOU PAY CASH
FOR THEM?

594
00:26:01,628 --> 00:26:03,798
YES.
HOW DID YOU --

595
00:26:03,830 --> 00:26:05,870
WELL, YOUR HUSBAND
TOOK YOUR CREDIT CARDS.

596
00:26:05,898 --> 00:26:09,898
JOLENE, DO YOU SOMETIMES
BUY THINGS

597
00:26:09,936 --> 00:26:13,766
TO MAKE YOURSELF FEEL BETTER --
CLOTHING OR JEWELRY?

598
00:26:16,008 --> 00:26:18,008
[ Crying ]
I AM SO SORRY.

599
00:26:19,779 --> 00:26:22,619
AND DID YOU NEED THOSE SHOES
SO BADLY

600
00:26:22,649 --> 00:26:24,849
THAT YOU STOLE MONEY
TO BUY THEM?

601
00:26:24,884 --> 00:26:26,994
YES.

602
00:26:27,019 --> 00:26:29,719
I THOUGHT THAT'S
WHAT THIS WAS ABOUT.

603
00:26:29,756 --> 00:26:31,616
I'LL PAY BACK EVERY PENNY.

604
00:26:31,658 --> 00:26:33,788
PLEASE.
DON'T TELL MY HUSBAND.

605
00:26:36,663 --> 00:26:39,673
COMPULSIVE BUYING
DISORDER.

606
00:26:42,735 --> 00:26:45,705
Roger: ONE OF OUR AGENTS SHOWED
JOLENE'S PHOTO TO THE DESK CLERK

607
00:26:45,738 --> 00:26:47,008
AT THE HOTEL
WHERE THE GOLD CARD WAS USED.

608
00:26:47,039 --> 00:26:48,779
SAID HE'S NEVER
SEEN HER BEFORE.

609
00:26:48,808 --> 00:26:51,638
BUT A DIFFERENT WOMAN
CHECKED IN REGULARLY

610
00:26:51,678 --> 00:26:53,008
USING JOLENE'S NAME,
MET FRANK THERE.

611
00:26:53,045 --> 00:26:55,875
BOTH WOMEN HAVE BLACK HAIR,
BUT ACCORDING TO THE DESK CLERK,

612
00:26:55,915 --> 00:26:57,745
THE OTHER ONE IS
"WAY HOTTER."

613
00:26:57,784 --> 00:27:01,854
I WAS RIGHT THE FIRST TIME.
"MOLE" MEANS "IMPOSTER."

614
00:27:01,888 --> 00:27:03,918
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

615
00:27:03,956 --> 00:27:07,856
MAYBE THIS IMPOSTER GOT HERSELF
A WIG OR A DYE JOB,

616
00:27:07,894 --> 00:27:09,864
DID SOMETHING
TO MAKE HERSELF LOOK

617
00:27:09,896 --> 00:27:12,026
ENOUGH LIKE JOLENE'S
DRIVER'S-LICENSE PHOTO

618
00:27:12,064 --> 00:27:13,974
TO FOOL ANYONE WHO DIDN'T
LOOK TOO CLOSELY.

619
00:27:25,812 --> 00:27:28,752
SHE MADE CHARGES EVERY
TUESDAY AND THURSDAY LAST MONTH

620
00:27:28,781 --> 00:27:30,951
AT A PLACE
CALLED THE RED RABBLE.

621
00:27:30,983 --> 00:27:33,793
THAT'S A BAR OFF I-90.

622
00:27:33,820 --> 00:27:35,690
AND TODAY'S THURSDAY.

623
00:27:35,722 --> 00:27:37,822
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYS IN DISTANCE ]

624
00:27:44,731 --> 00:27:48,071
THAT'S RIGHT, PROFESSOR.
I'M FOLLOWING YOU.

625
00:27:48,100 --> 00:27:50,940
HOW DO YOU LIKE
MY NEW AMERICAN CAR?

626
00:27:52,038 --> 00:27:53,908
Kate: DANIEL?

627
00:27:53,940 --> 00:27:55,040
WHAT'S GOING ON?

628
00:27:56,108 --> 00:27:57,808
LOOK.

629
00:27:57,844 --> 00:27:59,084
A BLUE CAMARO.

630
00:27:59,111 --> 00:28:01,711
THE SAME TYPE OF CAR
PARKED OUTSIDE OF OLENA'S

631
00:28:01,748 --> 00:28:02,818
THE NIGHT SHE DISAPPEARED.

632
00:28:02,849 --> 00:28:04,949
EXCUSE ME!

633
00:28:05,985 --> 00:28:07,715
HI, EVERYBODY!

634
00:28:07,754 --> 00:28:09,824
LISTEN, I...

635
00:28:09,856 --> 00:28:11,916
WAS BACKING UP
IN THE PARKING LOT,

636
00:28:11,958 --> 00:28:15,828
AND I KIND OF SORT OF HIT
A BLUE CAMARO.

637
00:28:15,862 --> 00:28:17,962
SO WHOSEVER CAR THAT IS,

638
00:28:17,997 --> 00:28:20,827
I WILL TOTALLY PAY FOR
THE DAMAGE, AND I AM SO SORRY.

639
00:28:20,867 --> 00:28:22,767
YEAH, THAT'S MY CAR.

640
00:28:25,071 --> 00:28:26,741
HOW BAD IS IT?

641
00:28:26,773 --> 00:28:28,743
IT'S PRETTY BAD.
[ CHUCKLES ]

642
00:28:28,775 --> 00:28:31,005
FBI.
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

643
00:28:31,043 --> 00:28:33,153
[ PATRONS MURMURING ]

644
00:28:37,083 --> 00:28:40,853
I WAS THERE,
BUT I DIDN'T KILL OLENA.

645
00:28:40,887 --> 00:28:42,887
I LOVED HER.

646
00:28:46,025 --> 00:28:49,025
I GOT A SIDE GIG
INSTALLING SATELLITE DISHES.

647
00:28:49,061 --> 00:28:50,961
IT PAYS FOR MY MUSIC.

648
00:28:50,997 --> 00:28:54,067
A COUPLE MONTHS AGO, I PUT IN
A DISH AT OLENA'S HOUSE.

649
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:56,770
SHE WAS LONELY.

650
00:28:56,803 --> 00:28:59,013
WE TALKED AND STARTED
SEEING EACH OTHER.

651
00:28:59,038 --> 00:29:00,868
SHE WOULD NEVER
SPEND THE NIGHT.

652
00:29:00,907 --> 00:29:02,977
SHE ALWAYS HAD TO GET HOME
BEFORE FRANK DID.

653
00:29:03,009 --> 00:29:04,979
SHE TOLD ME THAT SHE WAS
GONNA LEAVE HIM.

654
00:29:05,011 --> 00:29:07,781
WELL, MAYBE YOU REALIZED
THAT WAS NEVER GONNA HAPPEN,

655
00:29:07,814 --> 00:29:10,784
SO YOU GOT ANGRY
AND YOU KILLED HER.

656
00:29:10,817 --> 00:29:13,917
NO! NO, SHE WAS SUPPOSED TO
COME OVER AND NEVER SHOWED.

657
00:29:13,953 --> 00:29:16,023
SHE DIDN'T
PICK UP HER PHONE.

658
00:29:16,055 --> 00:29:18,985
I GOT SCARED THAT FRANK
MAYBE FOUND OUT ABOUT US
AND MAYBE HE HURT HER.

659
00:29:19,025 --> 00:29:20,155
I DROVE OVER.

660
00:29:20,192 --> 00:29:23,032
NO ONE ANSWERED THE DOOR,
SO I BROKE IN.

661
00:29:23,062 --> 00:29:26,172
BUT OLENA WASN'T THERE.

662
00:29:26,198 --> 00:29:28,028
AND THEN FRANK CAME IN.

663
00:29:28,067 --> 00:29:29,867
AND HE TURNED ON
THE LIGHTS.

664
00:29:29,902 --> 00:29:32,812
HE RUSHED ME, SO I GRABBED
A LAMP AND I HIT HIM.

665
00:29:32,839 --> 00:29:34,939
AND THEN
I GOT THE [BLEEP] OUT OF THERE.

666
00:29:34,974 --> 00:29:37,014
THAT'S A VERY COMPELLING
STORY, JAKE,

667
00:29:37,043 --> 00:29:39,013
EXCEPT IT DOESN'T EXPLAIN
ONE THING.

668
00:29:39,045 --> 00:29:41,075
HOW DOES JOLENE GREY
FIT IN?

669
00:29:41,113 --> 00:29:42,923
WHO?

670
00:29:42,949 --> 00:29:44,819
SUPER-HOTTIE,

671
00:29:44,851 --> 00:29:46,021
BLACK HAIR.

672
00:29:46,052 --> 00:29:47,192
COMES TO SEE YOU PLAY

673
00:29:47,219 --> 00:29:49,819
EVERY THURSDAY NIGHT
AT THE RED RABBLE.

674
00:29:49,856 --> 00:29:51,186
LOTS OF PEOPLE
COME TO HEAR US.

675
00:29:51,223 --> 00:29:53,193
ARE YOU THINKING
WHAT I'M THINKING?

676
00:29:53,225 --> 00:29:55,025
EXCEPT JOLENE
WAS HAVING AN AFFAIR

677
00:29:55,061 --> 00:29:56,831
WITH OLENA'S HUSBAND,
FRANK.

678
00:29:56,863 --> 00:29:58,973
NOW, IT CANNOT JUST BE
A COINCIDENCE.

679
00:29:58,998 --> 00:30:01,168
I BET YOU KNOW
WHO THE MOLE IS NOW.

680
00:30:03,135 --> 00:30:05,835
I DON'T KNOW
ANY JOLENE GREY.

681
00:30:05,872 --> 00:30:08,072
ACTUALLY, YOU DO.

682
00:30:08,107 --> 00:30:10,237
YOU -- YOU KNOW HER
INTIMATELY.

683
00:30:18,284 --> 00:30:21,994
Kate: MR. PRENTICE, CAN YOU
HELP US I.D. THIS WOMAN?

684
00:30:23,022 --> 00:30:24,162
Frank: NO. WHO IS SHE?

685
00:30:24,190 --> 00:30:26,260
THERE ANYTHING ABOUT HER
THAT'S FAMILIAR TO YOU?

686
00:30:26,292 --> 00:30:27,932
HER HAIR, MAYBE?

687
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:29,230
NO.
WHY -- WHY WOULD I --

688
00:30:29,261 --> 00:30:33,031
YOU'VE BEEN HAVING AN AFFAIR
WITH THIS WOMAN FOR MONTHS.

689
00:30:34,166 --> 00:30:35,996
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT'S [BLEEP]

690
00:30:36,035 --> 00:30:38,165
WELL, MAYBE HER NAME WILL
RING A BELL -- JOLENE GREY?

691
00:30:40,206 --> 00:30:41,306
NO. I-I DON'T KNOW.

692
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:43,240
YOU'VE BEEN PAYING OFF
HER CREDIT CARDS.

693
00:30:43,275 --> 00:30:44,275
WE HAVE THE RECORDS.

694
00:30:49,215 --> 00:30:53,185
OKAY, SO I BOUGHT JOLENE
SOME NICE STUFF.

695
00:30:53,219 --> 00:30:56,259
WHAT? ARE YOU SAYING
SOMEBODY KILLED HER?

696
00:30:56,288 --> 00:31:00,028
ACTUALLY, THE REAL JOLENE GREY
IS VERY MUCH ALIVE.

697
00:31:00,059 --> 00:31:03,199
YEAH, SHE LIVES OUT
IN THE 'BURBS WITH HER FAMILY.

698
00:31:03,229 --> 00:31:05,129
THIS WOMAN
STOLE HER IDENTITY.

699
00:31:05,164 --> 00:31:07,204
SHE WORE A WIG TO MAKE SURE
YOU WOULDN'T RECOGNIZE HER --

700
00:31:07,233 --> 00:31:08,373
VERY MUCH LIKE THIS ONE.

701
00:31:10,002 --> 00:31:13,172
I'LL BET
YOU RECOGNIZE HER NOW.

702
00:31:13,205 --> 00:31:16,205
YOU PUT A WIG ON A CORPSE?
WHAT KIND OF SICK --

703
00:31:16,242 --> 00:31:18,112
THAT'S OLENA.

704
00:31:18,144 --> 00:31:21,154
YOU WERE HAVING AN AFFAIR
WITH YOUR OWN WIFE, FRANK.

705
00:31:23,015 --> 00:31:24,215
THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE.

706
00:31:24,250 --> 00:31:26,120
ACTUALLY, IT IS.

707
00:31:26,152 --> 00:31:29,022
OLENA MUST HAVE FIGURED OUT OVER
TIME THAT YOU WERE FACE-BLIND,

708
00:31:29,055 --> 00:31:31,985
SO SHE STOLE ANOTHER WOMAN'S
IDENTITY AND SEDUCED YOU.

709
00:31:32,024 --> 00:31:34,134
SHE WAS PRACTICALLY
A PRISONER IN YOUR HOME,

710
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:36,230
SO SHE USED YOUR CONDITION
AGAINST YOU

711
00:31:36,262 --> 00:31:38,062
TO BILK YOU
FOR CASH, JEWELS.

712
00:31:38,097 --> 00:31:41,067
I THINK SHE WAS PROBABLY
TRYING TO SAVE UP ENOUGH MONEY

713
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:43,300
TO GET AWAY FROM YOU,
BUT, UH, TURNS OUT

714
00:31:43,335 --> 00:31:46,105
YOU WEREN'T THE ONLY ONE
SHE WAS SCREWING.

715
00:31:47,239 --> 00:31:49,009
WHAT?

716
00:31:49,041 --> 00:31:50,341
YEAH, TURNS OUT
WHILE YOU WERE AWAY AT WORK,

717
00:31:50,376 --> 00:31:53,176
SHE WAS BANGING THE GUY WHO
INSTALLED YOUR SATELLITE DISH.

718
00:31:53,212 --> 00:31:56,082
HE TOLD US ALL ABOUT IT.

719
00:31:56,115 --> 00:31:57,315
THAT [BLEEP]

720
00:31:57,349 --> 00:31:59,349
YOU CAN'T REALLY BLAME HER
FOR WANTING A BOY TOY

721
00:31:59,385 --> 00:32:01,315
WHEN SHE WAS
HAVING TO SLEEP WITH YOU

722
00:32:01,353 --> 00:32:03,063
AS HERSELF
AND AS JOLENE.

723
00:32:03,089 --> 00:32:04,359
OLENA WAS NEVER
ABDUCTED, FRANK.

724
00:32:04,390 --> 00:32:07,190
THE REASON NOBODY COULD FIND HER
IS THAT WHEN YOU KILLED

725
00:32:07,226 --> 00:32:09,226
THE WOMAN YOU THOUGHT
WAS YOUR MISTRESS,

726
00:32:09,261 --> 00:32:11,231
YOU'D REALLY JUST MURDERED
YOUR OWN WIFE.

727
00:32:11,263 --> 00:32:13,033
T-THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

728
00:32:13,065 --> 00:32:15,095
HOTEL DESK CLERK
PUTS YOU IN THE SAME ROOM AS HER

729
00:32:15,134 --> 00:32:16,274
ON THE DAY OF THE MURDER.

730
00:32:25,311 --> 00:32:27,151
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

731
00:32:28,414 --> 00:32:30,154
I NEVER MEANT TO KILL HER.

732
00:32:31,150 --> 00:32:35,090
TELL US WHAT HAPPENED.
MAYBE I CAN HELP YOU.

733
00:32:37,256 --> 00:32:39,126
I TRIED TO END IT
WITH HER.

734
00:32:39,158 --> 00:32:41,088
SHE -- SHE WAS
BLEEDING ME DRY.

735
00:32:41,127 --> 00:32:43,097
I COULDN'T
AFFORD HER ANYMORE.

736
00:32:43,129 --> 00:32:45,359
I TOLD HER I WAS GONNA
NEED THE JEWELRY BACK
TO PAY OFF YURI,

737
00:32:45,397 --> 00:32:47,327
OR ELSE
HE WAS GONNA TAKE OLENA.

738
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:51,370
BUT JOLENE WOULDN'T LISTEN,
YOU KNOW?

739
00:32:51,403 --> 00:32:54,373
NO. SAID SHE WAS NOTHING
WITHOUT ME.

740
00:32:54,406 --> 00:32:57,136
THEN SHE
STARTED TO HIT ME.

741
00:32:57,176 --> 00:32:59,106
I LOST IT.

742
00:33:05,117 --> 00:33:07,187
WHAT ABOUT THE BODY?

743
00:33:08,420 --> 00:33:10,390
I WAITED
UNTIL AFTER DARK,

744
00:33:10,422 --> 00:33:12,262
TOOK HER DOWN IN
THE MAINTENANCE ELEVATOR,

745
00:33:12,291 --> 00:33:13,461
AND TOSSED HER
IN THE DUMPSTER.

746
00:33:16,462 --> 00:33:19,372
IT'S TOO BAD WE CAN'T CHARGE YOU
WITH TWO MURDERS.

747
00:33:22,501 --> 00:33:24,101
Paul: DANIEL.

748
00:33:24,136 --> 00:33:25,096
OH, HEY, PAUL.

749
00:33:25,137 --> 00:33:27,137
DON'T "HEY, PAUL" ME.

750
00:33:27,173 --> 00:33:29,113
YOU KNOW, YOU REALLY BLEW IT
WITH HATHAWAY.

751
00:33:29,141 --> 00:33:31,281
WHY WOULD YOU WANT A FRAUD LIKE
THAT ON THE FACULTY, ANYWAY?

752
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:33,110
THAT FRAUD
IS AN ACADEMIC SUPERSTAR.

753
00:33:33,145 --> 00:33:35,105
EVERYBODY WANTS HIM --
HARVARD, NORTHWESTERN --

754
00:33:35,147 --> 00:33:37,417
BUT I AM GONNA GET HIM,
AND YOU'RE GONNA HELP ME DO IT.

755
00:33:37,449 --> 00:33:38,449
HERE.

756
00:33:38,484 --> 00:33:40,194
CUBS TICKETS.

757
00:33:40,219 --> 00:33:41,449
NOW, YOU'RE GONNA APOLOGIZE
TO HATHAWAY,

758
00:33:41,487 --> 00:33:43,417
AND YOU'RE GONNA INVITE HIM
TO TONIGHT'S GAME

759
00:33:43,455 --> 00:33:45,155
AS A PEACE OFFERING.

760
00:33:45,191 --> 00:33:47,331
COME ON, DANIEL.ILL.

761
00:33:47,359 --> 00:33:49,159
I REALLY NEED YOU
TO DO THIS FOR ME.

762
00:33:54,466 --> 00:33:57,166
COME ON, MAN.
YOU LOVE THE CUBBIES.

763
00:33:58,504 --> 00:34:00,444
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

764
00:34:00,472 --> 00:34:01,472
DANIEL.

765
00:34:02,474 --> 00:34:04,184
[ SIGHS ] KATE.

766
00:34:04,210 --> 00:34:05,480
HI.
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

767
00:34:05,511 --> 00:34:08,481
FRANK PRENTICE IS TAKING A PLEA
AND COOPERATING AGAINST YURI.

768
00:34:08,514 --> 00:34:10,224
THAT'S GREAT.

769
00:34:10,249 --> 00:34:12,219
AND IF WE CAN GET YURI
TO ROLL ON TUPELOV,

770
00:34:12,251 --> 00:34:15,451
THEN WE'LL HAVE THE UKRAINIANS
AND OLENA'S KILLER IN ONE SHOT.

771
00:34:15,487 --> 00:34:17,457
DO YOU LIKE BASEBALL?

772
00:34:17,489 --> 00:34:18,459
YEAH, SURE.

773
00:34:18,490 --> 00:34:20,190
I MEAN, WHO DOESN'T LIKE

774
00:34:20,226 --> 00:34:22,286
A COLD BEER AND A HOT DOG
AT A BALLGAME, RIGHT?

775
00:34:22,328 --> 00:34:25,198
WELL, I-I, UH,
JUST HAPPEN TO HAVE

776
00:34:25,231 --> 00:34:28,431
TWO, UH, TWO TICKETS
TO THE CUBS GAME TONIGHT.

777
00:34:29,435 --> 00:34:31,565
THAT SOUNDS GREAT.
WHAT TIME?

778
00:34:34,273 --> 00:34:35,513
[ CROWD CHEERING ]

779
00:34:37,509 --> 00:34:39,449
[ OVERLAPPING VOICES ]

780
00:34:44,216 --> 00:34:45,376
HAVE FUN.

781
00:34:46,552 --> 00:34:49,362
WAIT, YOU'RE NOT GOING?

782
00:34:49,388 --> 00:34:50,458
UH, NO.

783
00:34:51,523 --> 00:34:53,393
CROWDS DRIVE ME CRAZY.

784
00:34:53,425 --> 00:34:54,425
AH.

785
00:34:56,228 --> 00:34:57,258
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

786
00:34:57,296 --> 00:34:58,596
THANKS.

787
00:34:59,598 --> 00:35:01,268
ARE YOU STALKING ME?

788
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:02,270
OH, MY GOD.

789
00:35:02,301 --> 00:35:03,441
[ BOTH CHUCKLHI.

790
00:35:03,469 --> 00:35:05,539
I COULD ASK YOU
THE SAME QUESTION.

791
00:35:05,571 --> 00:35:07,371
LAST CHANCE
TO BUY ME THAT DRINK.

792
00:35:07,406 --> 00:35:08,406
I LEAVE TOWN TOMORROW.

793
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:11,240
UH, YOU KNOW, I'M SORRY.

794
00:35:11,277 --> 00:35:13,207
I DON'T THINK I CAN.
I HAVE PLANS.

795
00:35:13,245 --> 00:35:14,575
BUT TRAVEL SAFE.

796
00:35:18,417 --> 00:35:20,417
ACTUALLY, UM...

797
00:35:23,255 --> 00:35:24,415
DO YOU LIKE BASEBALL?

798
00:35:27,326 --> 00:35:29,396
Natalie:
WHY DIDN'T YOU TAKE KATE?

799
00:35:31,430 --> 00:35:34,270
BECAUSE I'D RATHER
WATCH IT ON TV...

800
00:35:34,300 --> 00:35:35,370
WITH YOU.

801
00:35:35,401 --> 00:35:37,501
SOMETHING'S BOTHERING YOU.

802
00:35:39,271 --> 00:35:40,571
IT'S OLENA.

803
00:35:40,606 --> 00:35:42,536
I JUST --
I CAN'T FIGURE OUT

804
00:35:42,574 --> 00:35:45,384
HOW A YOUNG GIRL
WHO BARELY SPOKE ENGLISH

805
00:35:45,411 --> 00:35:47,481
PULLED OFF
SUCH A COMPLICATED SCAM.

806
00:35:47,513 --> 00:35:49,483
I GUESS
SHE HAD EVERYONE FOOLED.

807
00:35:49,515 --> 00:35:51,445
Man: FOUL BALL
DOWN THE THIRD-BASE SIDE.

808
00:35:51,483 --> 00:35:53,423
OUT OF PLAY.

809
00:35:53,452 --> 00:35:55,492
WHOA.
GREAT CATCH BY THAT FAN.

810
00:35:55,521 --> 00:35:58,491
OH, I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

811
00:35:58,524 --> 00:36:00,294
SHE TOOK THAT [BLEEP]

812
00:36:00,326 --> 00:36:01,486
AND HE CATCHES
A FOUL BALL.

813
00:36:01,527 --> 00:36:03,327
YOU KNOW HOW MANY GAMES
I WENT TO AS A KID,

814
00:36:03,362 --> 00:36:05,432
AND I NEVER ONCE
CAUGHT A FOUL BALL?

815
00:36:05,464 --> 00:36:08,334
DANIEL, YOU HAVE NO ONE
TO BLAME BUT YOURSELF.

816
00:36:08,367 --> 00:36:09,467
THAT COULD HAVE BEEN YOU.

817
00:36:09,501 --> 00:36:11,641
BUT INSTEAD,
YOU LET HIM TAKE YOUR PLACE.

818
00:36:15,674 --> 00:36:17,684
SHE TOOK HER PLACE.

819
00:36:20,512 --> 00:36:22,452
THERE'S ANOTHER MOLE.

820
00:36:22,481 --> 00:36:25,281
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

821
00:36:25,317 --> 00:36:26,287
WHO ARE YOU CALLING?

822
00:36:26,318 --> 00:36:27,418
KATE.

823
00:36:27,453 --> 00:36:28,593
ARE YOU TRYING TO RUIN
HER DATE?

824
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:30,460
[ BUTTONS CLICKING ]

825
00:36:30,489 --> 00:36:33,489
I'M GONNA TELL HER
OLENA ISN'T DEAD.

826
00:36:41,867 --> 00:36:43,737
YOU TAKING EVERYTHING?

827
00:36:43,769 --> 00:36:45,939
MRS. PRENTICE IS DEAD, AND
MR. PRENTICE GO TO JAIL, SO --

828
00:36:45,971 --> 00:36:47,971
IT'S OKAY. NO ONE'S
ACCUSING YOU OF STEALING.

829
00:36:48,006 --> 00:36:50,036
IT ALL BELONGS TO YOU,
ANYWAY, DOESN'T IT...

830
00:36:51,877 --> 00:36:52,907
...OLENA?

831
00:36:53,912 --> 00:36:55,682
LISTEN,
FRANK PRENTICE IS A PIG.

832
00:36:55,714 --> 00:36:57,824
WE DON'T BLAME YOU
FOR WANTING TO MAKE HIM PAY.

833
00:36:57,849 --> 00:37:00,889
WHAT WE COULDN'T FIGURE
OUT WAS HOW YOU DID
IT ALL ON YOUR OWN.

834
00:37:00,919 --> 00:37:02,849
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING --

835
00:37:02,888 --> 00:37:04,018
I REMEMBERED YOU MENTIONED

836
00:37:04,055 --> 00:37:06,015
A COUSIN THAT FRANK
DIDN'T LIKE -- PAULINA.

837
00:37:08,794 --> 00:37:12,834
EVER SINCE WE WERE LITTLE GIRLS
IN UKRAINE, PAULINA PROTECT ME.

838
00:37:12,864 --> 00:37:14,904
AND NOW SHE PROTECTED YOU
FROM FRANK.

839
00:37:16,935 --> 00:37:19,865
SHE MARRIED AMERICAN, TOO,
FIVE YEARS BEFORE,

840
00:37:19,905 --> 00:37:22,735
BUT SHE DIVORCE HIM,
STAY IN COUNTRY.

841
00:37:22,774 --> 00:37:25,714
I CALL HER,
ASK HER TO COME.

842
00:37:25,744 --> 00:37:27,714
IT WAS SO GOOD TO SEE HER.

843
00:37:27,746 --> 00:37:30,716
SHE STAYED FOR A FEW DAYS.

844
00:37:30,749 --> 00:37:34,719
BUT SOON WE NOTICE
SOMETHING STRANGE.

845
00:37:34,753 --> 00:37:38,763
MY HUSBAND SOMETIMES --
HE THINK PAULINA IS ME.

846
00:37:50,035 --> 00:37:53,735
WHEN NEXT TIME SHE COME
TO VISIT, HE NOT RECOGNIZE HER,

847
00:37:53,772 --> 00:37:55,072
EVEN THOUGH HE KNOW HER.

848
00:37:55,106 --> 00:37:57,736
THAT'S WHEN SHE REALIZED
HE WAS FACE-BLIND.

849
00:37:57,776 --> 00:37:59,906
AND SHE MAKE PLAN
TO GET HIS MONEY.

850
00:37:59,945 --> 00:38:04,075
BUT FIRST SHE NEED NEW NAME
SO HE DOESN'T GET SUSPICIOUS.

851
00:38:04,115 --> 00:38:08,945
SO SHE STEAL WALLET AT MALL,

852
00:38:08,987 --> 00:38:12,857
AND SHE MAKE HERSELF LOOK LIKE
WOMAN ON DRIVING LICENSE.

853
00:38:14,125 --> 00:38:18,125
HE'S NOT USED TO BEAUTIFUL WOMAN
PAYING ATTENTION TO HIM,

854
00:38:18,163 --> 00:38:24,043
SO HE GIVE HER MONEY, JEWELS,
ANYTHING SHE WANT.

855
00:38:24,069 --> 00:38:25,939
FOR ME, IT GET WORSE.

856
00:38:26,972 --> 00:38:28,912
I WANT TO RUN AWAY.

857
00:38:28,940 --> 00:38:32,980
BUT PAULINA SAY WE HAVE TO WAIT
UNTIL WE GET ALL FRANK'S MONEY

858
00:38:33,011 --> 00:38:36,781
AND THAT SHE HAVE NEW PLAN
TO PROTECT ME.

859
00:38:36,815 --> 00:38:41,845
I GIVE HER HAIRCUT, AND I GIVE
HER MY CLOTHES AND MY PERFUME.

860
00:38:42,954 --> 00:38:46,124
PAULINA IS STRONGER THAN ME.

861
00:38:46,157 --> 00:38:48,887
SHE MAKE FRANK
STOP HITTING HER...

862
00:38:50,095 --> 00:38:53,965
...AND SHE CONVINCE FRANK
TO HIRE UKRAINIAN MAID

863
00:38:53,999 --> 00:38:55,929
TO KEEP HER COMPANY.

864
00:38:55,967 --> 00:38:59,967
SO PAULINA
BECAME YOU AND JOLENE,

865
00:39:00,005 --> 00:39:01,835
AND YOU BECAME THE MAID.

866
00:39:01,873 --> 00:39:03,113
IT'S AN INGENIOUS PLAN.

867
00:39:03,141 --> 00:39:05,841
YOU ARE
GOING TO ARREST ME.

868
00:39:06,912 --> 00:39:08,152
YOU'RE AN ACCESSORY
TO FRAUD.

869
00:39:08,179 --> 00:39:10,819
THE U.S. ATTORNEY'S OFFICE
MIGHT WANT TO CHARGE YOU,

870
00:39:10,849 --> 00:39:12,819
BUT I'LL DO MY BEST
TO CONVINCE THEM

871
00:39:12,851 --> 00:39:15,091
THAT BEING MARRIED
TO AN ABUSIVE, CHEATING MURDERER

872
00:39:15,120 --> 00:39:17,020
WAS PROBABLY
PUNISHMENT ENOUGH.

873
00:39:20,058 --> 00:39:21,858
THANK YOU.

874
00:39:21,893 --> 00:39:25,133
BUT MY HUSBAND WILL FIND OUT
WHAT WE DID TO HIM,

875
00:39:25,163 --> 00:39:27,873
AND WHEN HE LEAVE PRISON,
HE WILL FIND ME,

876
00:39:27,899 --> 00:39:28,829
AND WITHOUT PAULINA --

877
00:39:28,867 --> 00:39:30,037
YOU WERE THREATENED

878
00:39:30,068 --> 00:39:32,168
BY A KNOWN ASSOCIATE
OF THE TUPELOV ORGANIZATION.

879
00:39:32,203 --> 00:39:33,973
I CAN MAKE
A PRETTY GOOD CASE

880
00:39:34,005 --> 00:39:35,905
THAT YOU BELONG
IN WITNESS PROTECTION.

881
00:39:35,941 --> 00:39:39,041
YOU'LL GET A FRESH START, OLENA.
NEW NAME, NEW LIFE.

882
00:39:42,213 --> 00:39:43,853
Paul: DANIEL!

883
00:39:43,882 --> 00:39:45,852
PAUL, LOOK,
I KNOW YOU'RE UPSET.

884
00:39:45,884 --> 00:39:46,924
UPSET? NO, NO, NO.

885
00:39:46,952 --> 00:39:49,052
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU SAID TO HATHAWAY,

886
00:39:49,087 --> 00:39:51,887
BUT SUDDENLY
HE IS IN LOVE WITH THIS TOWN.

887
00:39:51,923 --> 00:39:54,933
HE'S TAKING THE JOB.
YOU DID GOOD, BUDDY.

888
00:39:54,960 --> 00:39:59,870
Daniel: WALT WHITMAN WROTE,
"I CONTAIN MULTITUDES."

889
00:39:59,898 --> 00:40:01,998
TURNS OUT HE WAS MORE RIGHT
THAN HE KNEW.

890
00:40:02,033 --> 00:40:03,903
THE SELF IS REALLY A COLLECTION

891
00:40:03,935 --> 00:40:06,035
OF SEVERAL
